summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fourteenth Avenue Northwest from East Forty-fifth to East Fifty-sixth Street et al in the City of Seattle, by grading, curbing, and constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 14976, creating Local Improvement District No. 1330 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
